         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JMR">
            <p>Elpis ?made these things [ . . . ] has been buried in this [?tomb . . .] property and [ . . . ?says farewell] to those who pass by [ . . . ] and virtue [ . . . ] 
               grapevine [ . . . ] and beauty [ . . . ] grace [ . . . ]</p>
